<P>Exhibitor registration opens July 15, 2008, but in the meantime, there's plenty for you to do. Check out the all-new <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/" target=_blank>CESweb.org</A>, which includes many rich, interactive features to help attract top-quality attendees for you.<BR></P>
